Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.92,0:00:13.26,Show Title,,0,0,0,,{\fs142.5\fnGallow Tree\4aFF\pos(443.949,598.286)}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Shocker is coming,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.69,0:00:18.78,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,with its armies\Nstraight from hell
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.32,0:00:22.88,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Their black shadows\Nthreaten us all
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:26.59,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,but I'll fight to maintain\Nthe peace of our world!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.59,0:00:30.26,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Go! Go! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.26,0:00:33.30,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,With my shining machine...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.85,0:00:36.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.45,0:00:40.11,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.02,0:00:44.70,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:48.32,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.32,0:00:50.97,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.87,0:00:54.49,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.49,0:00:59.13,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider, Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.13,0:01:02.56,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider, Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.60,0:01:11.17,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi is the Kamen\NRider, a cyborg.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.17,0:01:13.29,Narrator,,0,0,0,,He was modified by the evil\NShocker, a secret
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.29,0:01:15.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,organization plotting\Nworld domination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:18.71,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider has pledged to\Nfight Shocker and free humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs165\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(597.167,160.389)}The Monstrous
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.85,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscx100\fs155\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\b1\pos(467.167,710.389)}Namazugiller's Electric Hell
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.42,0:01:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.74,0:01:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,This is JW-20.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.19,0:01:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Unregistered submarine sighted 50\Nnautical miles off the Boso Peninsula.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.73,0:01:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This is JW-20.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.56,0:01:49.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So Shocker's Japan Branch base\Nis beneath Namegawa Island...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.39,0:02:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell...\Nyou've chosen a truly brilliant location.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.66,0:02:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on. The flamingo\Ndance is starting soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.16,0:02:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.02,0:02:24.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.94,0:02:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get going!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.55,0:02:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, Chairman!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.89,0:02:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, slow down, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.95,0:02:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, Doctor Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.15,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami... having you all the way\Nfrom the South America Branch to join us
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:53.21,Default,,0,0,0,,will be a true boon for\Nthe Shocker Japan Branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.56,0:03:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,But are they saying I can't handle\Nthe conquest of Japan all by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Allow me to show you\Nwhat I've brought.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.62,0:03:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.30,0:03:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Namazugiller,\Ncreated from the electric catfish
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,that live in the waters\Nof the Andes Mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Namazugiller?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.73,0:03:41.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... what can it do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough, Doctor Shinigami!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.33,0:04:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You've made your point.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.90,0:04:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The whiskers of the cyborg\NNamazugiller can channel 100,000 volts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.38,0:04:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Any human who touches those whiskers\Nwill be electrocuted instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even the Kamen Rider\Ncan stand against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:23.40,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi, suspicious of the JSDF\Nfighter that went down over the Boso Sea,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.40,0:04:27.31,Narrator,,0,0,0,,headed for the Boso Peninsula,\Naccompanied by FBI agent Taki Kazuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:43.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Isn't it beautiful?\N- What a great dancer...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.11,0:04:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.16,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.41,0:04:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,But boy,\Nflamingos have nice legs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.42,0:04:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't say that in\Nfront of a lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You little brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.75,0:05:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll pay for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,- Stop it, Goro!\N- Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.32,0:05:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, darn it! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go that way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:23.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Which way'd they go?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.85,0:05:30.95,Default,,0,0,0,,This way, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.96,0:05:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You scared me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.51,0:05:38.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.46,0:05:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost him in the tunnels!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.75,0:05:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.10,0:05:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You lost him in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.52,0:05:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's our necks on the line\Nif he gets himself lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.27,0:05:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Those caves are big, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.42,0:05:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.49,0:05:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi! Tokko!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.78,0:05:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I promise I forgive\Nyou, so please come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.32,0:06:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.73,0:06:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Show yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.67,0:06:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.28,0:06:19.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.43,0:06:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be my first\Nvictim here in Japan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.22,0:06:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.87,0:06:38.66,Default,,0,0,0,,This boy could make\Na valuable hostage
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.66,0:06:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,to lure out Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.08,0:06:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,We cannot kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.67,0:06:44.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.28,0:06:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me where to find him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.88,0:06:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be here soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.22,0:06:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Be patient until then.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.71,0:07:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,An emergency call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.03,0:07:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo here. Over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.38,0:07:10.16,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hongo? Goro's gone missing\Non Namegawa Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.16,0:07:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.08,0:07:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You think...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just what you think!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.58,0:07:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.47,0:07:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker has taken that\Nannoying brat hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.57,0:07:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're back in\NJapan, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.96,0:07:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,If you value the child's life,\Nyou must leave here at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.30,0:07:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You coward!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.88,0:07:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.57,0:07:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.66,0:07:46.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.78,0:07:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.50,0:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.53,0:07:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fish in a barrel now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.21,0:07:58.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Grenades! Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.71,0:08:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.23,0:08:11.20,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo! What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.20,0:08:12.38,Italics,,0,0,0,,What was that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.38,0:08:14.28,Italics,,0,0,0,,Hongo! Respond!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You've shown\Nyourselves, Shocker...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.21,0:08:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Namazugiller... come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There you are... Shocker cyborg!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.98,0:08:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Do what you've been longing for,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.08,0:09:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,and kill Hongo Takeshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.62,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I came from the\NAndes to destroy you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.71,0:09:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Namazugiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.52,0:09:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That must have been\Na pretty long trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.48,0:09:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me, Namazugiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.73,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.31,0:09:34.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.60,0:09:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy's body is now\Ncharged with 50,000 volts.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.12,0:10:14.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.30,0:10:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll put your power to the test!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Try me, Namazugiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.70,0:11:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.51,0:11:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Namazugiller...\Nthat's enough for now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.65,0:11:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Withdraw, so we can\Nembark upon our next plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider...\Nyou were lucky this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.47,0:11:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm afraid we'll have to\Nfinish this another time!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.55,0:11:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.81,0:11:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Namazugiller...\Na fearsome opponent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.93,0:11:45.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider,\Nis that the new Shocker cyborg?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.69,0:11:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give him a beating\Nthe next time I see him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.72,0:11:55.65,Bumper Episode 53-69,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fs90\pos(280,94)\c&H05008E&}KAMEN RIDER
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.48,0:12:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,My mission in Japan\Nis now complete.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We need only wait for Hongo\Nand Taki to walk into our trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.68,0:12:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You've done well, Doctor Shinigami,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.91,0:12:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but leave the rest in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.83,0:12:21.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ambassador Hell...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.65,0:12:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Namazugiller's power\Nis not without limits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.99,0:12:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You must reflect\Nsunlight off that tower
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.44,0:12:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,to recharge Namazugiller's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.51,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do not forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.23,0:12:54.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops, where's Goro?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So Shocker was\Ntelling the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.24,0:13:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Shocker?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.34,0:13:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We were attacked\Non our way here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.42,0:13:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops,\Nthey've taken Goro hostage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hongo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Pops and the others are\Nfast asleep in the hotel...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.73,0:14:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Should we really be\Nwasting time here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.25,0:14:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We know that Shocker\Nhas a base in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.27,0:14:14.25,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll try something\Non us sooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,- Goro!\N- Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.36,0:14:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.22,0:15:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Tokko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.19,0:15:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Emi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.43,0:15:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What in the world happened here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.05,0:15:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.52,0:15:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It went perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.79,0:15:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take them away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.41,0:15:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let it happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... so that's their game.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Is it okay to touch him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.01,0:15:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I can withstand a\Nlittle electricity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.88,0:15:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And the charge has\Nleft Goro's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.40,0:15:56.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what they\Nused to control him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,They put an electric\Ncharge in a human body
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:16:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,to create a high\Nvoltage discharger.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,If we hadn't interfered, they'd have\Nelectrified the others the same way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.54,0:16:04.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:13.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.65,0:16:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's safe now, Pops.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.94,0:16:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You two meanies!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.32,0:16:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You left me in that tunnel!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.07,0:16:21.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.60,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro must have been\Nattacked in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.66,0:16:30.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki, I'll go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.06,0:16:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'll go this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.93,0:16:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.49,0:16:42.14,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like we're\Nunder the ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the entrance\Nto their base?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.71,0:16:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.56,0:17:00.70,Default,,0,0,0,,This place will be\Nyour graveyard...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.70,0:17:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Just go quietly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:11.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.78,0:17:14.54,Default,,0,0,0,,This tunnel shouldn't\Nlead to the shore.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.60,0:17:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo here. Respond.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.23,0:17:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.90,0:17:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll electrify this man,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.45,0:17:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and force him to\Nfight Hongo Takeshi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.67,0:17:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.21,0:17:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.69,0:18:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.55,0:18:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hongo... die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.76,0:18:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki! Have you gone mad?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.46,0:18:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Taki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.43,0:18:27.63,Italics,,0,0,0,,Strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.63,0:18:30.02,Italics,,0,0,0,,There's a powerful electric current\Nrunning through Taki's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I, Namazugiller, will finish you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.87,0:18:48.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The charge has left his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.99,0:18:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this, Namazugiller!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.71,0:18:52.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You persistent fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.79,0:19:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.38,0:19:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Increase the voltage further!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.98,0:20:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If I raise it any higher,\Nhe won't last two minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.91,0:20:08.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.19,0:20:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs stronger electricity\Nto defeat the Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.23,0:20:19.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I need more electricity!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.59,0:20:23.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,I see... he's receiving\Nthe current from there?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.65,0:20:24.65,Italics,,0,0,0,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Goro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.23,0:20:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard them talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.48,0:20:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,When I was in Shocker's base,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:42.91,Default,,0,0,0,,they said they had to reflect\Nthe sun's light off that tower,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,to give that catfish\Nmonster more power.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.94,0:20:53.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Light... give me light!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.60,0:20:54.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.17,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.94,0:21:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone! Tie it down, then run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.17,0:21:33.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Emergency, sir!\NThe reflectors won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.95,0:21:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.92,0:21:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be...\Ninvestigate at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Give my body the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.88,0:21:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.03,0:22:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.62,0:22:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Rider Reverse Kick!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.73,0:22:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you, Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.92,0:22:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well...\Nthey're having a good time.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.75,0:22:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.29,0:22:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.76,0:22:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Where'd Hongo get off to?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.29,0:22:57.73,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Hongo Takeshi, the Kamen\NRider, defeated the
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.73,0:22:59.96,Narrator,,0,0,0,,terrible electrical\Nmonster Namazugiller.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.96,0:23:03.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,But anywhere he goes,\Nhe'll find a new monster spreading evil,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:05.50,Narrator,,0,0,0,,courtesy of Shocker's ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.09,0:23:10.84,Cont,,0,60,0,,{\blur.8\fad(0,400)}To be continued
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.03,0:23:13.48,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\4aFF\bord0\b1\fs67.5\fnCalibri\pos(499.031,496.481)}Next Episode Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.79,0:23:14.84,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The next assassin sent by Shocker\NHQ to kill our Kamen Rider
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.84,0:23:16.72,Narrator,,0,0,0,,is the monstrous Harinezuras.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.72,0:23:19.68,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A Shocker transport carrying\Na killer virus crashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.68,0:23:22.13,Narrator,,0,0,0,,A peaceful fishing village\Nis dragged into the chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.13,0:23:24.74,Narrator,,0,0,0,,The Kamen Rider must face a\Nnew monster's killer needles.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:28.80,Narrator,,0,0,0,,Join us next week for "The Monstrous\NHarinezuras' Killer Skull Plan."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:31.07,NEP AND TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\fscy90\fs105\bord0\fnCienfuegos\4aFF\1c&HF3F4F4&\b1\pos(457.167,724.389)}The Monstrous Harinezuras'\NKiller Skull Plan
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.97,0:23:40.81,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,He came here on a storm...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.39,0:23:43.39,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is he? Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.39,0:23:45.35,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Who is this man of storms,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.35,0:23:48.40,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,who sends the\Nvillains scattering?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.90,0:23:50.77,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.77,0:23:52.65,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,His mask stands for justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.65,0:23:54.44,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Start it up! Rev it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.44,0:23:55.89,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Get that engine running!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.16,0:23:58.28,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Give me top speed, Cyclone!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.33,0:24:04.05,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Hit them with\Nall of your anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.05,0:24:07.58,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Put an end to Shocker's evil!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.58,0:24:11.18,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Rider! Rider!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.67,0:24:15.50,LYRICS,,0,0,0,,Kamen Rider!
Comment: 0,0:01:19.89,0:01:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous\NNamazugiller's Electric Hell
Comment: 0,0:23:28.80,0:23:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Monstrous Harinezuras'\NKiller Skull Plan